OL,3,CTwo men charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter man seriously injured in shooting
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged with
OL,7,Fattempted murder after a shooting in
OL,8,FSwindon left a man with serious
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,FEmergency services were sent to St
OL,12,FPaul's Street in Gorse Hill at around
OL,13,F9pm on Friday, 19 June to reports of a
OL,14,Fshot being fired.
OL,16,FA man in his 30s had sustained serious
OL,17,Finjuries. He remains in hospital in a
OL,18,Fstable but critical condition.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
