OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782280080
OL,3,CTwo men charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter man seriously injured in shooting
OL,6,FDylan Anthony, 19, and Kyron Anthony,
OL,7,F20, both of Milton Road, Swindon, have
OL,8,Fbeen charged with attempted murder and
OL,9,Fpossessing a firearm with intent to
OL,10,Fcause fear of violence.
OL,12,FThey have both been remanded in
OL,13,Fcustody and are due to appear at
OL,14,FSwindon Magistrates Court today (24
OL,15,FJune).
OL,17,FSix others arrested in connection with
OL,18,Fthe incident have been released on
OL,19,Fbail pending further enquiries.
